call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: George (LAC) throws an errant pass out of bounds.
Doncic (DAL) bring his hand to the side, and not underneath the basketball while dribbling on the perimeter.
Bullock (DAL) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Powell (DAL) and Zubac (LAC) both quickly engage and disengage in marginal arm contact before Powell attempts to set the pick on the perimeter.
Powell (DAL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during George's (LAC) driving shot attempt.
George (LAC) briefly grasps Powell's (DAL) lower body but immediately releases while defending around the pick set on the perimeter. Powell's FOM is not affected.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself in George's (LAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Batum (LAC) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Powell (LAC) establishes himself in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Doncic (DAL) moves alongside George's (LAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Powell (LAC) commits a take foul on Bullock (DAL).
Hardaway Jr (DAL) commits a take foul on Batum (LAC).
Morris Sr. (LAC) enters the lane prior to Batum (LAC) releasing his free throw.
Covington (LAC) is the last to touch the ball which is correctly awarded to Dallas.
